org.apache.wicket.session.ISessionStore
public class CwmSessionStore
extends org.apache.wicket.protocol.http.SecondLevelCacheSessionStore

A session store that adds a listener to do cleanup of CwmSession objects. Also watches the session size and warns about it if it is too large.
